# MSD Risk Survey Demo #

A lightweight, low-code **Streamlit** application that helps safety professionals and small businesses **identify, assess, and control** musculoskeletal disorder (MSD) risks in manual handling, pushing/pulling, and repetitive tasks.

Providing an intuitive, no-database interface for the New Zealand risk assessment standards (NZMAC, NZRAPP, NZART).

